{"tid":549751,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［世界大戰］搭地鐵會唔會讓座畀大肚婆？？？","createTime":"2018-02-04T03:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T15:54:41.000Z","uid":56716,"like":234,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"e10d495cc824248e06fadca1012020c40b3c654c","tid":549751,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"尋日喺fb見到個大肚舊同學屌鳩香港人冷漠，戴哂口罩著哂平底鞋肚凸凸咁企喺佢地面前都唔讓座，然後有幾個應該係人母朋友留言一齊圍爐屌鳩香港人。<br />\n本身如果我見到大肚婆個肚蘿咁大都會讓嘅（睇唔到就無計），但睇見佢地挺住已被中出嘅非純潔身軀喺度屌鳩啲唔關事嘅人，我以後見到大肚婆都唔讓座了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申青頭</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3effd78e10328e4b4bf69841e7877060d225084","tid":549751,"uid":63670,"like":439,"dislike":9,"score":430,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......<br />\n我會讓既<br />\n大肚跌一跌真係可能一屍兩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讓下又無壞既<br />\n廢老不了"},{"pid":"d9443a68effbc78f8bb58ec2d7b8d66af5ee1422","tid":549751,"uid":11506,"like":61,"dislike":12,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"陣間佢唔係大肚只係肥嘅話讓俾佢又話歧視肥人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6a6754b7e98abbf368a98269371597e05ad3a6","tid":549751,"uid":16061,"like":63,"dislike":163,"score":-100,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒 個胎我有份？點解要其他人為你付出？"},{"pid":"f21fba2c6431144454094b64f7bf92180a94ffab","tid":549751,"uid":79893,"like":264,"dislike":8,"score":256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"大肚啫<br />\n唔係啞咗啊嘛<br />\n想坐唔撚識得出聲問㗎<br />\n我係佢肚入面條蟲?"},{"pid":"efea4819d8c70d5ef88772edb7727c8bbed76870","tid":549751,"uid":24641,"like":42,"dislike":7,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"f21fba2c6431144454094b64f7bf92180a94ffab","tid":549751,"uid":79893,"like":264,"dislike":8,"score":256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"大肚啫<br />\n唔係啞咗啊嘛<br />\n想坐唔撚識得出聲問㗎<br />\n我係佢肚入面條蟲?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"其實係 老馮人地留意到咁<br />\n明明地鐵都有啲大肚婆貼紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a16a13af3e70dc6b2beabfb7a9725b0e3167e93","tid":549751,"uid":56716,"like":66,"dislike":5,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......<br />\n我會讓既<br />\n大肚跌一跌真係可能一屍兩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讓下又無壞既<br />\n廢老不了</blockquote><br />\n我本身都覺得讓下無壞，但佢地個心覺得係老奉，人地可能睇唔到/有其他原因需要坐呢，但就恃住自己大肚覺得自己大曬要所有人讓佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50d66bd6a774476b86a8f429320b64290b4a8a3","tid":549751,"uid":130904,"like":62,"dislike":76,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老柒柒 個胎我有份？點解要其他人為你付出？</blockquote><br />\n祝你性無能<br />\n俾你搵到人捐精都祝你條女流產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呀 不過睇你條撚樣應該連女都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b7f5d54fbe90b9e8ea4b210db4b0fa2b35431b","tid":549751,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":9,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:45:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8af6aaecfef6aaaa32e6c8969e0229543757244b","tid":549751,"uid":828,"like":133,"dislike":1,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"有次見到個阿伯讓座俾個肥婆 應該係以為佢大左肚<br />\n個肥婆係咁灑手話唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個阿伯仲想扶佢坐 <br />\n睇到我笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a988e9ca3040e0165b5c97146d8f9842fee24d15","tid":549751,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完內文以為係小多士出post</block