018-02-04T05:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想坐呀？想坐要出聲先得架 你唔講我又點知你想坐呀 無理由你想坐我又唔讓 你唔想坐我又讓俾你架嘛 大家講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢有需要開到聲我一定會讓，有時真係會睇唔到/唔知佢大肚定肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcadbffe378fce4a810dce84f6fbf0f965d67bb6","tid":549751,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>廢老 細蚊仔 大人抱bb都唔會讓<br />\n但大肚婆一定讓</blockquote><br />\n我而家都好少坐了，除非返工拎住袋制服好重先會坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>今晚諗住去食井飯 有無介紹</blockquote><br />\n無呀好少食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁凍都唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f929372e14f9c334c0b1c582564b362c7708bbd","tid":549751,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蝗蟲唔會<br />\n<br />\n港媽會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會專登讓比西面肥婆</blockquote><br />\n我有個做空姐嘅朋友同欣宜差不多身型，啲人成日以為佢大肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讓座比佢地<br />\n<br />\n佢起會發癲但又唔可以鬧人<br />\n<br />\n幾好玩<br />\n<br />\n坐低再問佢BB仔定女"},{"pid":"0c31e643c8747a9241059277c456980c8fcc0a6a","tid":549751,"uid":33770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:01:55.000Z","msg":"讓你就人情<br />\n唔讓就道理<br />\n屌人唔撚讓嗰班撚樣<br />\n抵難產死<br />\n一屍兩命<br />\n<br />\n利申 會讓"},{"pid":"33c8f93f5784129b0abb06e386c043f22f68c268","tid":549751,"uid":152759,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"上次坐係到恰下恰下 跟住有個大肚婆態度極惡劣咁講 起身啦，見唔到我大肚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1094ca8d975533f18f426bcb541ebc66c4ee6fc","tid":549751,"uid":3695,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"老野同大肚婆最仆街 <br />\n老野大撚把時間，想坐可以搭倒頭車去總站。大肚婆最撚賤，屌你老母又唔係我搞大你個肚，點解要我付出代價?你老公搞大你個肚咪叫你老公讓坐囉，再唔係你咪揀個有司機車你出入既老公囉。喂，你屌又唔比我屌，仲要我讓坐，我前世姦撚左你呀? <br />\n你大唔大肚係有得揀，但我讓唔讓坐無得揀?我屌你老母，屌你老公呀!!!"},{"pid":"f882cb2346b377ca09809afedb5046ce77b5ab22","tid":549751,"uid":42434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"香港大肚婆就一定讓<br />\n支那大肚蟲就叫佢食撚屎"},{"pid":"316400d9a461b634f59eedc863b5abd216fe4349","tid":549751,"uid":8199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"如果係我前面咪起身去隔離企<br />\n坐唔坐佢自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65295aebd45854e5a7638d2888ba19dcd1aa553","tid":549751,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:11:38.000Z","msg":"處女我就讓<br />\n大肚腩  不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0ac4c8ed37c10c8684325456819c8009931b02","tid":549751,"uid":10538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:17:20.000Z","msg":"我會大大聲問佢 你係咪想坐？想坐出聲呀嘛"},{"pid":"8a2fd38f2cb834b25ed7c683ff6cafec94604e55","tid":549751,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"充斥道德撚嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f385f4cbcc70f4e981ee362b4a9e1bd51336111","tid":549751,"uid":25003,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好垃圾，好似全世界欠撚咗你<br />\n到底咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7304c29750de9498c02282526df8a57d47ab18","tid":549751,"uid":45232,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"其實啲廢老 大肚婆係咪全部啞<br />\n根本你肯禮貌開聲問<br />\n十個有八個都會讓俾你<br />\n<br />\n又要做老舉又要拎貞節牌坊"},{"pid":"662b5f912f3c6a511404c68b737526cb38746633","tid":549751,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:51:21.